            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> finely</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cider vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to a bowl with a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>warm water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> to the bowl and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
