      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper and cut into quarters lengthways – these are your <strong>lettuce wedges</strong></p>",
